Sort-Key-Top
============

This module provides a set of functions that allows to select the top
n elements from a list using several common orderings and custom key
extraction procedures.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

        Test::More for testing


